.SH NAME
iio_trigger_validate_own_device \- Check if a trigger and IIO device belong to the same device
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" iio_trigger_validate_own_device
.BI "(struct iio_trigger *trig "  ","
.BI "struct iio_dev *indio_dev "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "trig" 12
The IIO trigger to check
.IP "indio_dev" 12
the IIO device to check
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
This function can be used as the validate_device callback for triggers that
can only be attached to their own device.
.SH "RETURN"
0 if both the trigger and the IIO device belong to the same
device, -EINVAL otherwise.
